text: Aleksej Demjanov (born 9 December 1973) is a Croatian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Croatia Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Cherkessk
